headline: How The Uber Technologies (UBER) Story Is Shifting As Analysts Reset Valuations And Expectations
summary: Uber Technologies is back in focus after an updated analyst fair value estimate moved slightly from US$105.36 to US$104.47 per share. Research notes tie this change mainly to refreshed models and sector wide multiple resets, with many analysts still weighing optimism on execution and growth against questions around valuation, macro risk and regulation. As you read on, you will see how these shifting price targets fit into the broader story and what to watch as the Uber narrative evolves. Stay...
